                        <p>Editorial constrains prevent me from continuing in this vein, but I have 17 more points. However, a full pr&eacute;cis will be appearing in the October issue of the Journal of Social History, and I encourage all interested parties to give it their consideration.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Rob Goodman is a Trinity senior.</p>
